<br />
On the etched crest... I spoke to a friend of mine that I hadn't seen in a long time... and who's in the elemental planes.  He had a hard time finding the book and gave up..... and already had the 2nd gem.... so I didn't even need the hate bones... he just MQ'd the 2nd gem to me as I already had the concordance of black magic, and he said he's got something better for that slot now.
<br />

<br />
What's funny about this, is I was with him when the crest fell for him a long time ago.   And I lost the roll.... so in a way... I guess I did win the roll.... just took a long time to get it.  LOL
