				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The King is higher level than the other named in the Inner Sanctum.  He's at least level 61.  The other nameds' levels require that you use a level 44 pet to pet-pull them.  The King can be pulled with a L49 pet, as long as you aren't using a Staff of Mastery.
<br />

<br />
The "if the pet is green, we can pull it." theory is correct, in my experience, with no exceptions.<br />_________________<br />Arhallia Ironborne
