				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">As a resident farmer of hate, ihave seen every piece for every class marsinger drop and off of dang near every mob... go 2 Concordances in 1 day not 2 weeks ago off of Arcanist V'Gimis (tier 4), I got mine off Sorcerer C'Gazin, have seen them drop off non caster mobs also, such as Spy Master I'Kavin (tier 4) and Evangelist W'Rixxus (tier 3).... 
<br />

<br />
You definitely have a better chance of getting a Signet from a tier 1 mob, Crest from tier 2 mob, Concordance from tier 3 mob and all the final books from tier 4 mobs... HOWEVER, ANY named at all *CAN* drop ANY piece at all at any given time... Of course you also have a better chance of getting a caster item off a caster and a melee item off a melee mob but it certainly is NOT limited to such.  Normally we hold down 5-6 named spawns in tier 3/4 for several hours, our most in 1 sitting was 6 named.  all told it took me 4 months to get to Gem4 but seems like now that we're up there regularly we're moving people thru gems even faster, the roadblock is always the Concordance for gem3, regardless of class.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=608950" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.divinesilence.shattering.us/sigs/thayetsig.jpg" border="0" /></a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
